description:
From VHS transfer, Chick Corea shares tips and tricks with practice and composition. 

Last section of the video features a live composition session with John Patitucci (electric bass) and Tommy Brechtlein (drums). 

Link to accompanying PDF doc with sheet music: https://rebrand.ly/chickcorea .
